* Four New Widget Styles: Meet "WavyGradientDots," "RotatingColorGradient," "SnowCone," and "ElongatedBeat"! Each style offers a unique look with dynamic animations and layouts.
* Style Refinements: The "GoldenDust" style now features smoother transitions and more consistent colors.
* Quick Widget Config: Long-pressing the in-app widget now always opens the configuration screen for easy customization.
* Bug Fix: Fixed an issue where the double-tap to seek gesture was too sensitive.